{"id": "3aff301cf02c7ec2ecefca3bdc8fbf3b36bfae333f7b149f97fc917d6ffdd435", "item_id": "74ddd9b55e:0", "text": "RenderMan 会将 Houdini particles（粒子）渲染为球体。"}
{"id": "f19969b916c22ad99d1b735a0944c6b11c3c41d1325561d53f40019f65d85a4a", "item_id": "74ddd9b55e:1", "text": "点缩放由"}
{"id": "99ea701c3d90beef4ab574f64ea18167bed0dcd84f7c0758281246a6ff856368", "item_id": "74ddd9b55e:2", "text": "pscale"}
{"id": "4ff35663b2257e0f909ba825f9017d3bf428aa03759e6425f1499879b1cdef6b", "item_id": "74ddd9b55e:3", "text": "primvar 控制。添加名为 \"pscale\" 的几何属性。使用"}
{"id": "07bcf2ba3fc58d2f3e672317fe1cc9fabc64d2369b79a8a2d76e4611b1c879a6", "item_id": "74ddd9b55e:4", "text": "PxrPrimvar"}
{"id": "0c93817113450d9ff8b30063986fd2f3bb9cd106751bb147468a23ae299a8748", "item_id": "74ddd9b55e:5", "text": "在网络中读取该值。除此之外，我们也支持标准的"}
{"id": "33b3873bbb73bb7421ef3718a68931a5173d7cc4a322dd6765d4c4726ebece9a", "item_id": "74ddd9b55e:6", "text": "Houdini attributes（Houdini 属性）"}
{"id": "98d4fc8263f2d22fd545b0f4000185876e402d7c9b21eec0b04eee3216229236", "item_id": "74ddd9b55e:7", "text": "并可通过 PxrPrimvar 或"}
{"id": "f10fea6a2ec17bb10b85ccea83fad5b30941f17adc83469c3f3d73bc50b43f37", "item_id": "74ddd9b55e:8", "text": "PxrAttribute"}
{"id": "4f17ed50223bc45db989f194ed8ec427f7eb7ab9020eb0fcbf712f16a0f03bac", "item_id": "74ddd9b55e:9", "text": "在 shading networks（着色网络）中处理。"}
{"id": "1c707f8357ac7b96dd8c897a41fae6b2492818c492470e7bf0066cfb1f50ffe1", "item_id": "74ddd9b55e:10", "text": "若要创建 uniform scale（统一缩放），也可以在对象级别的"}
{"id": "60c1d829f536d1fdf08fa8a04aa459864b8ba9ef7b65158119fae2d53253912a", "item_id": "74ddd9b55e:11", "text": "RenderMan > Geometry Specific > Points"}
{"id": "83c19797af969f92d78861a642ea1cd155e023d444359c7e50ffba4b522efede", "item_id": "74ddd9b55e:12", "text": "选项卡下使用 Width 参数。当几何体上存在 pscale 属性时，此属性会被忽略。"}
{"id": "63fed85554b0f078dc0a926008adb5b159a5fcb2fe7ec842ba4d626613b7db87", "item_id": "74ddd9b55e:13", "text": "Width：指定以像素为单位测量的 uniform width（统一宽度）"}
{"id": "283a31e8c7696d587d0de63deec3bd324def58d88f8a79938dd89f7ffde78564", "item_id": "74ddd9b55e:14", "text": "Falloff Power：允许用户柔化 particles（粒子）的边缘"}
{"id": "53c41de126b284043bf1bfae6ce745ad054d0b1aa9fc97224fa962633681da1b", "item_id": "74ddd9b55e:15", "text": "其他 RenderMan 几何值会显示在 Geometry Tab 中，但会被忽略。"}
